需向交通廳登記。<br />\n<br />\n交通事務局局長林衍新向澳門傳媒表示，有關行政程序仍在處理，未知何時正式簽署。<br />\n<br />\n據澳門媒體「愛瞞日報」報道，有關互認安排一直備受爭議，有意見擔心政策會讓更多合資格人士在澳駕駛，變相加重本澳交通壓力；亦有意見亦認為兩地駕駛文化不同，恐會增添澳門道路的安全隱患。新澳門學社早前提出，兩地駕照互認屬「重大政策」，建議澳門政府應先進行諮詢，但未獲當局接納。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:25:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母閪份報紙叫愛瞞"},{"pid":"17245f9781f736823e58874b02f57bef5944e420","tid":649153,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7e4d35c97414f2de34a5c0d8b74ca1fc30352eeb","tid":649153,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"有料嘅澳門人唔o係外國都o係香港喇"},{"pid":"3376a8d19ebd41a7cf4e3c26feed5f1bd56c21d3","tid":649153,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"Hk next <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19029a371342f356e255e395cd095cc26530103d","tid":649153,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ad9f7f2c03492d6344d9140ea9d9a80774f43c1","tid":649153,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30edc7166b9016aed2c1df90d7f169190807b662","tid":649153,"uid":39137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"咩叫相較其他地區？<br />\n氹仔同路環互認？"},{"pid":"df847de57a29d0ac23b4a5aa3766594b1ade6953","tid":649153,"uid":21225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"澳門啲路又窄又難認 點樣可以直接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35258509e58eff98f63c2d6c2d7eb9d2a143a53c","tid":649153,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"日日都格蘭披治大塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9706baaf608ad88a82a58b1f25c2ab450319f4","tid":649153,"uid":214